[IF_EXPRE] implement IF expression


[USE_BYTE] use byte[] instead of char[] to avoid conversion


[REMOVE_STRING_BUILDER] do not use StringBuilder anymore as they increment their capacity one by one
use our own array
write out own StringBuilder that increment its capacity more than by one


[EXTERNAL_URL] include virtual can call external website
Example:
<!--include virtual="http://www.dns.com/uri" -->
the call of the external URL should be asynchron

